### Policy Viewer API Endpoints Testing
### Base URL: http://localhost:3001/api/m365

# ============================================================================
# Policy Viewer Endpoints
# ============================================================================

### Get all policies for viewer
GET http://localhost:3001/api/m365/policies/viewer

### Get Intune policies only
GET http://localhost:3001/api/m365/policies/viewer?policyType=Intune

### Get Purview policies only
GET http://localhost:3001/api/m365/policies/viewer?policyType=Purview

### Get Azure AD policies only
GET http://localhost:3001/api/m365/policies/viewer?policyType=AzureAD

### Search policies by name or description
GET http://localhost:3001/api/m365/policies/viewer?searchTerm=compliance

### Get active policies only
GET http://localhost:3001/api/m365/policies/viewer?isActive=true

### Get inactive policies only
GET http://localhost:3001/api/m365/policies/viewer?isActive=false

### Get policies mapped to specific control (replace with actual control ID)
GET http://localhost:3001/api/m365/policies/viewer?controlId=3.5.3

### Get policies sorted by name
GET http://localhost:3001/api/m365/policies/viewer?sortBy=name&sortOrder=asc

### Get policies sorted by last synced date
GET http://localhost:3001/api/m365/policies/viewer?sortBy=lastSynced&sortOrder=desc

### Get policies sorted by type
GET http://localhost:3001/api/m365/policies/viewer?sortBy=type&sortOrder=asc

### Combined filters - Active Intune policies with search term
GET http://localhost:3001/api/m365/policies/viewer?policyType=Intune&isActive=true&searchTerm=device

### Get single policy detail (replace :id with actual policy ID)
GET http://localhost:3001/api/m365/policies/viewer/1

### Get viewer statistics
GET http://localhost:3001/api/m365/policies/viewer/stats

### Export policy data
GET http://localhost:3001/api/m365/policies/viewer/export

